WEBVTT

00:07.278 --> 00:10.741
FIND WHO DID THIS!

00:12.383 --> 00:15.216
AVENGE ME!

00:16.647 --> 00:22.323
AVENGE...ME...TOO!

00:22.323 --> 00:24.695
DON´T WORRY.

00:24.695 --> 00:27.598
WE´LL BE TOGETHER
 IN THE NEXT WORLD!

00:27.598 --> 00:33.134
UNLESS SALMA HAYEK
 GETS THERE BEFORE YOU.

00:33.134 --> 00:35.306
HEY, WE SAID
 "TILL DEATH DO US PART."

00:35.306 --> 00:37.308
AFTER THAT,
 YOU´RE ON YOUR OWN.

00:37.308 --> 00:39.740
COME ON, ANGIE, THIS IS
 MY FAVORITE HOLIDAY.

00:39.740 --> 00:42.343
MEXICANS TAKE HALLOWEEN
 TO THE NEXT LEVEL.

00:42.343 --> 00:44.145
WE GET TO DRESS UP
 LIKE SKELETONS.

00:44.145 --> 00:46.177
IT´S THE ONLY TIME
 OF THE YEAR WE´RE THIN.

00:46.177 --> 00:48.048
WAIT TILL YOU SEE
 WHAT I GOT PLANNED.

00:48.048 --> 00:50.581
THE TREATS ARE GONNA BE
 IN THIS BOWL,

00:50.581 --> 00:52.353
IF ANYONE CAN GET PAST...

00:52.353 --> 00:54.054
THE "TERROR-IER."

00:59.090 --> 01:02.563
DOES THE DEMON DOG
 WANT HIS BELLY RUBBED?

01:02.563 --> 01:04.565
YES, HE DOES.

01:04.565 --> 01:06.567
YES, HE DOES.

01:06.567 --> 01:08.669
STOP IT!

01:08.669 --> 01:12.273
YOU´RE DIMINISHING
 HIS EVIL.

01:12.273 --> 01:15.376
DAD, SHOW HER WHAT HAPPENS WHEN
 PEOPLE GET CLOSE TO THE CANDY!

01:20.281 --> 01:25.386
[ Spooky voice ] TAKE ONLY
 ONE CANDY! OOOH!

01:25.386 --> 01:27.688
MOM, DAD,
 TOBY´S LEAVING NOW.

01:27.688 --> 01:31.462
OH, HONEY, WE´RE SO SORRY
 YOU´RE MOVING TO OMAHA.

01:31.462 --> 01:32.693
THANKS.

01:32.693 --> 01:35.796
WE´RE ALL GONNA MISS YOU.

01:35.796 --> 01:37.328
OH!

01:37.328 --> 01:39.670
YEAH, BUT DON´T WORRY,
 WE´LL VISIT YOU UP THERE.

01:39.670 --> 01:40.771
REALLY? WHEN?

01:42.333 --> 01:45.376
LET´S NOT SPOIL
 THE SURPRISE.

01:45.376 --> 01:46.877
[ CAR HORN HONKS ]

01:46.877 --> 01:48.209
I GOT TO GO.

01:54.215 --> 01:56.787
I MADE THIS FOR YOU,

01:56.787 --> 01:59.620
SO YOU´LL NEVER FORGET ME.

01:59.620 --> 02:02.423
I´M REALLY GONNA MISS YOU.

02:03.224 --> 02:06.357
BYE.

02:06.357 --> 02:07.898
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

02:19.270 --> 02:20.641
THIS IS HORRIBLE.

02:20.641 --> 02:23.244
SHE JUST LOST
 HER BEST FRIEND.

02:23.244 --> 02:25.376
LET ME TALK TO HER.

02:34.925 --> 02:37.658
[ Spooky voice ] CARMEN...

02:37.658 --> 02:42.633
I KNOW YOU ARE GOING THROUGH
 SOMETHING VERY DIFFICULT.

02:42.633 --> 02:45.936
I KNOW I DON´T HAVE
 A HAND TO HOLD

02:45.936 --> 02:49.940
OR A SHOULDER TO CRY ON...

02:49.940 --> 02:52.603
BUT ANYTIME YOU WANT TO TALK,

02:52.603 --> 02:57.678
I´M HERE FOR YOU.

02:57.678 --> 03:02.883
OR WE COULD JUST WATCH
 "THE REAL WORLD."

03:02.883 --> 03:05.286
WHY DO THEY ALWAYS MAKE

03:05.286 --> 03:08.959
THE COWBOY AND
 THE BLACK GUY ROOMMATES?

03:11.762 --> 03:16.697
UH-OH! SOMEBODY ATE
 THE LESBIAN´S YOGURT.

03:16.697 --> 03:18.769
OOOH!

03:18.769 --> 03:20.301
[ SKULL CLATTERS ]

03:20.301 --> 03:22.633
[ INTRO TO WAR´S "LOW RIDER"
 PLAYS ]

03:33.384 --> 03:38.589
♫ ALL MY FRIENDS
 KNOW THE LOW RIDER ♫

03:39.620 --> 03:44.525
♫ THE LOW RIDER
 IS A LITTLE HIGHER ♫

04:08.979 --> 04:11.752
ALL RIGHT,
 I´LL HANDLE IT!

04:11.752 --> 04:13.023
WHAT´S UP?

04:13.023 --> 04:15.856
THE POWERS BROTHERS
 WANT ME TO FIRE REGGIE.

04:15.856 --> 04:18.789
WHAT´S THE PROBLEM?
 HE´S A TERRIBLE EMPLOYEE.

04:18.789 --> 04:20.731
I KNOW, BUT IF I FIRE HIM,

04:20.731 --> 04:24.495
I WON´T HAVE ANYBODY TO PLAY
 SANTA AT THE COMPANY PARTY.

04:27.538 --> 04:28.999
EXCUSE ME, SANTA.

04:28.999 --> 04:31.271
I GOT TO GO FIRE REGGIE.

04:33.574 --> 04:36.347
REGGIE, CAN I TALK TO YOU
 IN MY OFFICE?

04:36.347 --> 04:38.649
NO, GEORGE, I CAN´T.
 I GOT -- I GOT TO GET HOME.

04:38.649 --> 04:41.812
WE HAD A BIG FIRE.
 ALMOST THE WHOLE HOUSE.

04:41.812 --> 04:43.684
EVEN MY PARROT JANIE DIED.

04:43.684 --> 04:46.357
THE LAST THING
 THE FIREMEN HEARD WAS...

04:46.357 --> 04:48.058
"PRETTY BIRD!

04:48.058 --> 04:49.960
"PRETTY BIRD!

04:49.960 --> 04:51.822
PRETTY BIRD!"

04:53.994 --> 04:57.598
I´M SORRY, GEORGE.
 WHAT DID YOU WANT TO TELL ME?

04:57.598 --> 04:59.930
NOTHING.
 YOU BETTER GET GOING.

05:02.673 --> 05:04.705
HEY, I HEARD.

05:04.705 --> 05:08.379
THE COLONEL FRIES BIRDS EVERY
 DAY. NOBODY CRIES FOR THEM.

05:16.847 --> 05:19.420
SO, GIRLFRIEND...

05:19.420 --> 05:21.051
HOW YOU LIVING?

05:21.051 --> 05:22.092
GREAT.

05:22.092 --> 05:24.094
MAKING ANY FRIENDS?

05:24.094 --> 05:25.696
NOT TRYING.

05:25.696 --> 05:27.828
SO, WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO,
 SIT ON THE COUCH FOREVER?

05:27.828 --> 05:29.600
MAYBE.

05:29.600 --> 05:31.802
GONNA TAKE CARE OF US
 WHEN WE GET OLDER?
 WHATEVER.

05:33.063 --> 05:36.637
CARMEN, HONEY,
 I´M GOING TO THE MALL.

05:36.637 --> 05:38.909
YOU WANT TO COME WITH ME?

05:38.909 --> 05:42.473
I´LL BE IN MY ROOM
 WHERE IT´S QUIET.

05:44.375 --> 05:47.378
HEY! YOU GOT HER
 OFF THE COUCH!

05:47.378 --> 05:48.879
THIS ISN´T GOOD.

05:48.879 --> 05:50.451
COME ON, ANGIE.
 SHE´S A KID.

05:50.451 --> 05:52.423
SHE´S GOING THROUGH
 SOMETHING. LET HER.

05:52.423 --> 05:53.924
FOR NOW.
 BUT I´M TELLING YOU,

05:53.924 --> 05:55.986
SHE NEEDS TO GET OUT
 AND MAKE SOME NEW FRIENDS.

05:55.986 --> 05:58.689
I DIDN´T HAVE A LOT OF FRIENDS,
 AND I TURNED OUT FINE.

05:58.689 --> 06:00.891
I DID! I TURNED OUT FINE.

06:00.891 --> 06:05.936
HEY, YOU PASSED MY EXPECTATIONS
 WHEN YOU FINISHED SIXTH GRADE.

06:05.936 --> 06:08.399
WHAT´S 12 TIMES 12?
 144.

06:08.399 --> 06:10.701
EVERY TIME!

06:10.701 --> 06:12.603
AMAZING.

06:16.847 --> 06:18.679
Ernie: GEORGE,
 HAVE YOU SEEN REGGIE?

06:18.679 --> 06:21.381
IS HE STILL WALKING WITH THAT
 SHOE BOX FULL OF BIRD ASHES?

06:21.381 --> 06:25.486
YEAH! IT´S THE WEIRDEST
 THING -- IT RATTLES.

06:25.486 --> 06:28.659
THE BEAK DON´T BURN, ERNIE.
 THE BEAK DON´T BURN.

06:28.659 --> 06:31.061
THE POWERS BROTHERS
 ARE GONNA FIRE ME

06:31.061 --> 06:32.723
IF I DON´T FIRE REGGIE.

06:32.723 --> 06:35.065
I GOT TO DO IT NOW.

06:35.065 --> 06:36.667
ALL RIGHT.

06:36.667 --> 06:38.398
WHEN YOU HAVE A SECOND.

06:38.398 --> 06:39.700
SHH! SHH!

06:39.700 --> 06:42.633
YOU CAN´T LEAVE ME.

06:42.633 --> 06:46.006
NO, YOU CAN´T JUST THROW AWAY
 A MARRIAGE AFTER 10 YEARS!

06:46.006 --> 06:49.009
LISTEN, WHY DON´T
 WE JUST TALK --

06:49.009 --> 06:51.482
WHAT´S GOING ON, REGGIE?

06:51.482 --> 06:53.183
MY WIFE IS LEAVING.

06:53.183 --> 06:55.145
REGGIE...

06:59.189 --> 07:02.823
KEEP DOING
 YOUR THING, BROTHER.

07:02.823 --> 07:04.595
TILL FRIDAY.

07:06.627 --> 07:09.530
THANKS FOR MAKING
 MY COSTUME, GRANDMA.

07:09.530 --> 07:13.103
YEAH, WELL, YOU KNOW,
 I HAD 30 SECONDS TO KILL.

07:13.103 --> 07:15.005
THAT´S NICE, YEAH.

07:18.569 --> 07:20.110
OH, MAN.

07:20.110 --> 07:22.573
THAT IS ONE
 SCARY-ASS COSTUME.

07:24.044 --> 07:25.516
I LIKE YOURS TOO, MAX.

07:30.180 --> 07:32.052
GEORGE, WE GOT TO TALK.

07:32.052 --> 07:33.123
WHAT?

07:33.123 --> 07:34.525
IT´S BEEN TWO WEEKS!

07:34.525 --> 07:37.187
HEY, I WORK ALL DAY.
 I´M TIRED AT NIGHT.

07:37.187 --> 07:40.060
I CAN´T JUST TURN IT ON.

07:42.893 --> 07:45.195
I´M TALKING ABOUT CARMEN.

07:45.195 --> 07:47.938
HOW LONG ARE WE GONNA LET HER
 SIT UP THERE AND MOPE?

07:47.938 --> 07:49.239
KIDS NEED TO BE KEPT BUSY,

07:49.239 --> 07:51.602
OR SOONER OR LATER
 THEY GET INTO TROUBLE.

07:51.602 --> 07:54.144
A REPORT OUT SAYS THAT MOST
 UNDERAGE SEX, DRINKING,

07:54.144 --> 07:56.807
AND HOOLIGANISM HAPPENS
 BETWEEN 3:00 AND 6:00 P.M.

07:56.807 --> 07:58.078
HOOLIGANISM?!

07:59.149 --> 08:01.912
HOW OLD IS THAT REPORT?

08:01.912 --> 08:03.954
YOU KNOW WHAT
 SHE NEEDS TO DO?

08:03.954 --> 08:06.757
SHE NEEDS SOME
 EXTRACURRICULAR ACTIVITIES.

08:06.757 --> 08:08.088
OH, HERE WE GO AGAIN.

08:08.088 --> 08:11.021
I HAD A TON OF ACTIVITIES
 AND A TON OF FRIENDS.

08:11.021 --> 08:13.894
YES, MISS HOMECOMING QUEEN,
 HEAD CHEERLEADER,

08:13.894 --> 08:15.195
YEARBOOK EDITOR.

08:15.195 --> 08:17.497
BUT WHERE DID ALL THAT
 POPULARITY GET YOU?

08:17.497 --> 08:20.070
YOU MARRIED THE GUY
 WITH NO FRIENDS.

08:20.070 --> 08:22.973
FACE IT HONEY, YOU PEAKED.

08:22.973 --> 08:25.205
YOU CAN MAKE FUN,
 BUT I DIDN´T HAVE TIME

08:25.205 --> 08:27.538
TO SIT AROUND THE HOUSE
 AND DO NOTHING.

08:27.538 --> 08:29.710
AND CARMEN IS NOT
 GONNA DO THAT, EITHER.

08:29.710 --> 08:31.511
I WENT TO HER
 SCHOOL WEBSITE.

08:31.511 --> 08:34.144
LOOK! LOOK AT ALL THE STUFF
 THAT SHE COULD BE DOING.

08:34.144 --> 08:37.548
HOMECOMING COMMITTEE,
 SCHOOL NEWSPAPER,

08:37.548 --> 08:39.119
PEP SQUAD.

08:39.119 --> 08:40.751
THIS IS WHAT
 SHOULD HAPPEN --

08:40.751 --> 08:43.023
YOU SHOULD BACK OFF AND
 LET HER FIND HER OWN WAY.

08:43.023 --> 08:44.625
HOW LONG IS THAT
 GONNA TAKE?

08:44.625 --> 08:46.557
IF SHE´S
 ANYTHING LIKE ME,

08:46.557 --> 08:48.599
SHE SHOULD
 GET IT TOGETHER...

08:48.599 --> 08:51.001
LATE 30´s.

08:51.001 --> 08:54.034
I THINK WE NEED TO BE
 A LOT TOUGHER ON THIS GIRL.

08:54.034 --> 08:55.906
I AM TIRED
 OF BABYING HER.

08:55.906 --> 08:57.137
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

08:57.137 --> 08:58.308
I´M TAKING HER DINNER.

09:03.744 --> 09:05.145
CARMEN, DINNER´S HERE.

09:05.145 --> 09:06.316
YOU DIDN´T KNOCK!

09:06.316 --> 09:08.148
GEORGE, COME UP HERE!

09:08.148 --> 09:11.181
PUT THAT RIGHT WHERE IT WAS,
 AND DON´T MOVE A MUSCLE.

09:11.181 --> 09:13.624
WHAT´S WRONG?

09:13.624 --> 09:16.156
HAVE YOU LOST YOUR MIND?!
 WHERE DID YOU GET THOSE?

09:16.156 --> 09:19.229
I TOOK THEM FROM GRANDMA BENNY.
 I WAS JUST GONNA TRY ONE.

09:19.229 --> 09:21.992
EXACTLY WHAT TIME
 DID YOU TAKE THEM?

09:21.992 --> 09:25.636
I DON´T KNOW. SOMETIME AFTER
 3:00 AND BEFORE 6:00.

09:27.638 --> 09:29.299
WHAT´S ALL THE COMMOTION?

09:29.299 --> 09:32.943
GEORGE IS LETTING CARMEN
 FIND HER OWN WAY.

09:32.943 --> 09:36.076
LET HER FIND
 HER OWN SMOKES.

09:36.076 --> 09:39.610
YOU TWO,
 KEEP UP THE GOOD WORK.

09:48.689 --> 09:51.762
ANGIE, I UNDERSTAND
 WE GOT TO DO SOMETHING,

09:51.762 --> 09:53.163
BUT WHY PEP SQUAD?

09:53.163 --> 09:55.966
BECAUSE PEP SQUAD TEACHES YOU
 TEAMWORK, DISCIPLINE,

09:55.966 --> 09:57.327
YOU MAKE FRIENDS,

09:57.327 --> 09:59.930
AND YOU CAN´T CHEER WITH
 A CIGARETTE IN YOUR MOUTH.

10:04.334 --> 10:06.206
IT WALKS LIKE
 A CHEERLEADER.

10:06.206 --> 10:08.238
IT´S DRESSED LIKE
 A CHEERLEADER.

10:08.238 --> 10:10.681
IT´S IGNORING ME LIKE
 A CHEERLEADER.

10:10.681 --> 10:13.684
I HAD TO CALL IN A LOT OF FAVORS
 TO GET YOU ON THAT SQUAD.

10:13.684 --> 10:16.246
IT´S A LUCKY THING THAT
 OTHER GIRL TRANSFERRED OUT.

10:16.246 --> 10:17.748
I DON´T WANT TO DO THIS!

10:17.748 --> 10:20.390
CARMEN, STOP WORRYING!
 YOU´RE GONNA DO GREAT.

10:20.390 --> 10:22.793
THIS IS ALL YOU´VE GOT
 TO REMEMBER --

10:22.793 --> 10:24.094
WHEN YOU CLAP...

10:24.094 --> 10:26.156
SEND IT OUT...
 TO THE WORLD.

10:26.156 --> 10:28.328
SEND IT OUT...
 TO THE WORLD!

10:34.905 --> 10:37.107
[ SIGHS ]

10:37.107 --> 10:40.140
YOU STILL GOT
 YOUR OLD POM-POMS?

10:40.140 --> 10:43.113
´CAUSE I GOT SPIRIT,
 YES, I DO.

10:43.113 --> 10:47.217
I GOT FIVE MINUTES BEFORE
 WORK, HOW ABOUT YOU?

10:50.821 --> 10:52.222
BAD NEWS, DUDE.

10:52.222 --> 10:54.324
I GOT ANOTHER MEMO
 FROM THE POWERS BROTHERS.

10:54.324 --> 10:55.926
YOU´RE GONE.

10:55.926 --> 10:58.258
BUT YOU SAID PLANES
 NEED WINGS!

10:58.258 --> 11:00.260
I KNOW WHAT I SAID!

11:00.260 --> 11:01.862
BUT YOU´RE GONE.

11:01.862 --> 11:04.194
BUT I DON´T KNOW
 HOW TO DO ANYTHING ELSE.

11:04.194 --> 11:06.266
AND MY PARENTS
 COUNT ON MY INCOME.

11:06.266 --> 11:07.838
WE´LL BE OUT ON
 THE STREET!

11:07.838 --> 11:10.000
HEY, WE ALL
 GOT PROBLEMS, MAN.

11:10.000 --> 11:11.271
CLEAN OUT YOUR LOCKER.

11:15.145 --> 11:17.948
HOW WAS THAT, HUH?
 BELIEVABLE, RIGHT?!

11:17.948 --> 11:20.180
[ SNIFFLING ]
 NO!

11:20.180 --> 11:22.753
I KNEW
 YOU WERE KIDDING.

11:22.753 --> 11:24.314
[ SOBBING ]

11:26.256 --> 11:29.990
OKAY. NOW I´M READY.

11:31.992 --> 11:33.693
REGGIE,
 I NEED TO TALK TO YOU.

11:33.693 --> 11:35.726
GOOD, ´CAUSE I NEED
 TO TALK TO YOU, TOO.

11:35.726 --> 11:37.427
LET ME GO FIRST.
 DON´T INTERRUPT ME.

11:37.427 --> 11:39.900
OKAY, BUT I GOT GOOD NEWS.

11:39.900 --> 11:41.001
REALLY?

11:41.001 --> 11:42.472
I´M IN LOVE.

11:42.472 --> 11:44.204
IT´S AMAZING.

11:44.204 --> 11:45.906
I GO TO SEE A DIVORCE LAWYER.

11:45.906 --> 11:48.338
IT TURNS OUT TO BE
 MY HIGH-SCHOOL SWEETHEART.

11:48.338 --> 11:50.310
IT´S LIKE
 WE´VE NEVER BEEN APART.

11:50.310 --> 11:52.482
SO I´M GONNA GO GET
 A QUICKIE DIVORCE

11:52.482 --> 11:55.215
AND THEN WE ARE GOING
 TO VEGAS TO TIE THE KNOT.

11:55.215 --> 11:59.820
OH, MY HEART HAS WINGS,
 GEORGE, AND I´M FLYING!

11:59.820 --> 12:01.852
CONGRATULATIONS, MAN.
 THANKS.

12:01.852 --> 12:03.323
YOU´RE FIRED.

12:03.323 --> 12:06.496
WHAT? NO, NO.
 Y-YOU CAN´T FIRE ME, GEORGE.

12:06.496 --> 12:09.729
THINGS ARE JUST STARTING
 TO GO RIGHT.

12:09.729 --> 12:12.933
I KNOW. I´M SORRY.

12:12.933 --> 12:14.765
GOD, I FEEL TERRIBLE,
 REGGIE.

12:14.765 --> 12:16.807
THIS IS THE WORST WEEK
 OF MY LIFE!

12:16.807 --> 12:18.909
I GOT TO FIRE
 MY FAVORITE EMPLOYEE,

12:18.909 --> 12:20.340
MY DAUGHTER´S A HOOLIGAN,

12:20.340 --> 12:22.843
MY WIFE´S BEEN SENDING
 IT OUT TO THE WORLD.

12:24.875 --> 12:27.047
YOU MET MY MOM.

12:27.047 --> 12:28.518
[ SIGHS ]

12:28.518 --> 12:31.081
IT´S OKAY, BUDDY.

12:31.081 --> 12:33.083
I UNDERSTAND.

12:33.083 --> 12:34.955
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

12:34.955 --> 12:36.486
ARE YOU LEAVING?

12:36.486 --> 12:37.928
YEAH.

12:37.928 --> 12:39.389
[ SNIFFLES ]

12:39.389 --> 12:42.332
THEN I´M OKAY.

12:42.332 --> 12:44.935
[ WHISTLES ]

12:49.099 --> 12:52.002
All:
 RAVEN FANS, YELL "GO!" GO!

12:52.002 --> 12:55.005
RAVEN FANS, YELL "FIGHT!"
 FIGHT!

12:55.005 --> 12:56.506
GO, RAVENS! FIGHT!

12:56.506 --> 13:00.410
NO STOPPING US!
 ALL RIGHT!

13:00.410 --> 13:02.552
WHOO!WHOO!
 GO RAVENS!

13:02.552 --> 13:03.984
HI.

13:03.984 --> 13:05.555
HEY, YOU MUST BE CARMEN.

13:05.555 --> 13:07.257
EVERYBODY, MEET CARMEN.

13:07.257 --> 13:09.259
HI.HI.
 HI.HI.

13:09.259 --> 13:10.861
I GUESS
 IT´S A LITTLE WEIRD,

13:10.861 --> 13:12.792
ME GETTING IN
 ´CAUSE PATTI TRANSFERRED.

13:12.792 --> 13:15.365
DON´T WORRY ABOUT IT. PATTI
 DIDN´T REALLY GET TRANSFERRED.

13:15.365 --> 13:16.867
SHE GOT KNOCKED UP.

13:16.867 --> 13:19.229
BUT YOU LOOK GOOD
 IN HER UNIFORM.

13:19.229 --> 13:21.371
IT´S A LITTLE LOOSE
 IN THE FRONT.

13:21.371 --> 13:22.933
I GUESS PATTI WAS, TOO.

13:22.933 --> 13:24.574
[ LAUGHTER ]

13:24.574 --> 13:27.307
LOOK, WE KNOW YOU HAVE
 A LOT OF CATCHING UP TO DO,

13:27.307 --> 13:29.309
SO WE´LL DO SOMETHING
 SIMPLE FIRST.

13:29.309 --> 13:31.081
LET´S TRY A CALL
 AND RESPONSE.

13:31.081 --> 13:32.282
OKAY. WHAT DO I DO?

13:32.282 --> 13:34.414
WE´LL CALL OUT A LINE,
 THEN POINT TO YOU,

13:34.414 --> 13:37.888
AND YOU RESPOND WITH
 "IT´S TRUE, IT´S TRUE."

13:37.888 --> 13:40.390
LIKE, "WE´RE RAVENS,
 WE´RE TIGHT."

13:40.390 --> 13:42.552
IT´S TRUE, IT´S TRUE.

13:42.552 --> 13:44.294
IT´S TRUE, IT´S TRUE.

13:44.294 --> 13:46.296
AND REMEMBER WHEN YOU CLAP...
 SEND IT OUT TO THE WORLD?

13:46.296 --> 13:47.427
GOOD GIRL!

13:47.427 --> 13:49.129
READY? OKAY!

13:49.129 --> 13:51.201
WE´RE RAVENS, WE´RE TIGHT.

13:51.201 --> 13:53.163
IT´S TRUE, IT´S TRUE.
 IT´S TRUE, IT´S TRUE.

13:53.163 --> 13:55.165
All:
 YOU JEFF US, WE´LL FIGHT.

13:55.165 --> 13:57.037
IT´S TRUE, IT´S TRUE.
 IT´S TRUE, IT´S TRUE.

13:57.037 --> 13:58.838
THERE´S CARMEN, SHE´S NEW.

13:58.838 --> 14:00.540
IT´S TRUE, IT´S TRUE.
 IT´S TRUE, IT´S TRUE.

14:00.540 --> 14:04.214
HOW DID SHE GET HERE?
 WELL, WE´LL TELL YOU.

14:04.214 --> 14:07.978
HER MOMMY CAME CRYIN´,
 THE COUNSELOR WAS BUYING.

14:07.978 --> 14:10.150
AND NOW WE´RE STUCK
 WITH A LOSER WHO SUCKS.

14:10.150 --> 14:12.222
WHICH CARMEN?
 THAT CARMEN!

14:12.222 --> 14:14.424
IT´S TRUE.
 YOU KNOW IT´S TRUE.

14:18.428 --> 14:20.630
YOU´RE PRETTY FAST.
 TRY OUT FOR THE TRACK TEAM!

14:20.630 --> 14:22.632
[ LAUGHTER ]

14:23.964 --> 14:26.236
[ Imitating Bill Cosby ]
 DA-DA-DA.

14:26.236 --> 14:28.498
WHOA, MAN,
 CHECK IT OUT!

14:28.498 --> 14:33.573
THE HOT WITCH FILLING OUT
 THE CANDY BOWL, YOU SEE.

14:33.573 --> 14:35.205
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

14:35.205 --> 14:37.447
HEY, COS, YOU´RE ON DOOR DUTY
 UNTIL CARMEN GETS BACK.

14:37.447 --> 14:40.080
SHE´S PROBABLY OUT WITH
 HER PEP-SQUAD BUDDIES.

14:40.080 --> 14:42.482
NOW I´M IGNORING
 THE COCKY WITCH

14:42.482 --> 14:46.917
AND GOING OVER TO
 THE FRONT DOOR, DA-DA.

14:46.917 --> 14:48.488
TRICK OR TREAT!

14:48.488 --> 14:52.222
WELL, MAN, IT´S GOOD.
 AND THE JELL-O,

14:52.222 --> 14:54.594
AND THE SASSAFRAS.

14:54.594 --> 14:57.527
COME ON IN, KIDS,
 AND GET CANDY.

15:00.430 --> 15:03.573
DID YOU HAVE A STROKE
 LIKE MY GRANDPA?

15:03.573 --> 15:06.306
KIDS SAY
 THE DARNEDEST THINGS.

15:06.306 --> 15:07.907
GOODBYE, ARMY BOY.

15:07.907 --> 15:09.940
GOODBYE, SNOTTY PRINCESS.

15:09.940 --> 15:11.341
HEY!

15:11.341 --> 15:13.913
WE NEED ANOTHER PILLOWCASE.
 THIS ONE´S FULL!

15:13.913 --> 15:16.416
HEY, MAX, DO YOU
 WANT SOME WATER, HONEY?

15:16.416 --> 15:19.589
YOU MUST BE HOT
 UNDER THERE.

15:19.589 --> 15:21.191
YOU´RE NOT MY GRANDMA.

15:21.191 --> 15:23.323
OH, CRAP.

15:23.323 --> 15:24.955
I´LL BE RIGHT BACK!

15:24.955 --> 15:27.927
I´LL TAKE THE CAR,
 YOU GO DOOR TO DOOR.

15:27.927 --> 15:29.329
I LOST GRANDMA!

15:29.329 --> 15:33.563
OH! IT´S OKAY, HONEY.
 UH, GRANDMA´S FINE.

15:33.563 --> 15:35.265
BUT SHE HAS
 ALL MY CANDY!

15:35.265 --> 15:38.038
[ Normal voice ] YEAH,
 BUT SHE THINKS YOU´RE LOST,

15:38.038 --> 15:41.071
AND SHE´S REALLY WORRIED,
 AND THAT´S LIKE CANDY TO DADDY.

15:41.071 --> 15:44.174
OH! SO, HOW´D IT GO?

15:44.174 --> 15:45.575
I LEARNED A CHEER.

15:45.575 --> 15:48.348
WHEN I POINT TO YOU,
 YOU SAY, "IT´S TRUE, IT´S TRUE."

15:48.348 --> 15:51.481
THEY CALLED ME A LOSER ´CAUSE
 MOM GOT ME ON THE SQUAD.

15:51.481 --> 15:53.723
THEY HATE ME
 AND DON´T WANT ME THERE.

15:53.723 --> 15:55.185
OH, HONEY.

15:55.185 --> 15:56.626
DO ME A FAVOR --
 STAY OUT OF MY LIFE.

15:59.629 --> 16:02.162
I GOT TO GO TALK TO HER.

16:02.162 --> 16:04.634
NO. LET HER COOL OFF.
 I´LL GO UP THERE IN A MINUTE.

16:04.634 --> 16:06.096
Benny: GEORGE! GEORGE!

16:06.096 --> 16:08.138
HAS MAX SHOWN UP YET?!

16:08.138 --> 16:09.239
NO, MOM!

16:09.239 --> 16:11.341
OH, CRAP!

16:14.604 --> 16:17.207
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

16:17.207 --> 16:20.410
[ Imitating Bill Cosby ]
 DA DA-DA DA-DA.

16:20.410 --> 16:24.654
YOU KNOW WHAT WOULD MAKE YOU
 FEEL BETTER IS SOME PUDDING.

16:24.654 --> 16:26.556
THAT´S CANDY.

16:26.556 --> 16:30.690
I KNOW. I JUST LIKE
 SAYING THE WORD "PUDDING."

16:30.690 --> 16:32.592
YOU DON´T KNOW HOW
 HORRIBLE IT WAS.

16:32.592 --> 16:34.724
YOU´VE NEVER BEEN
 HUMILIATED LIKE THAT.

16:34.724 --> 16:37.567
[ Normal voice ] CARMEN,
 I KNOW HOW MEAN KIDS CAN BE.

16:37.567 --> 16:41.171
THESE GUYS IN MY NEIGHBORHOOD
 USED TO CALL ME "SPUDS."

16:41.171 --> 16:44.074
BECAUSE I WAS DARK,
 I HAD REALLY SHORT HAIR,

16:44.074 --> 16:45.635
MY HEAD WAS KIND OF LUMPY.

16:45.635 --> 16:48.007
I GUESS I LOOKED
 LIKE A POTATO.

16:48.007 --> 16:50.310
BUT THAT DIDN´T
 GIVE THEM A RIGHT

16:50.310 --> 16:53.113
TO HOLD ME DOWN
 AND BUTTER ME.

16:53.113 --> 16:56.316
WELL, MAYBE IF SOMEONE HELD
 MOM DOWN AND BUTTERED HER,

16:56.316 --> 16:58.448
SHE WOULDN´T HAVE
 MADE ME DO THIS.

16:58.448 --> 17:01.651
I BET NO ONE´S MADE FUN OF HER.
 SHE´S SO PERFECT.

17:01.651 --> 17:03.523
YOUR MOM WAS HAPPY
 IN HIGH SCHOOL,

17:03.523 --> 17:05.795
AND SHE THOUGHT PEP SQUAD
 WOULD DO THE SAME FOR YOU.

17:05.795 --> 17:07.196
BUT I´M NOT LIKE HER!

17:07.196 --> 17:09.729
YEAH, I KNOW.
 YOU´RE LIKE ME.

17:09.729 --> 17:11.731
DAMN, I´M SORRY.

17:11.731 --> 17:13.633
I THOUGHT I WAS GONNA MEET

17:13.633 --> 17:16.465
ALL THESE COOL PEOPLE
 IN HIGH SCHOOL.

17:16.465 --> 17:19.709
NOW EVERYBODY HATES ME.

17:19.709 --> 17:22.342
I MISS TOBY.

17:22.342 --> 17:24.544
I KNOW, BUT YOU
 GOT TO BELIEVE ME

17:24.544 --> 17:27.146
WHEN I TELL YOU EVERYTHING´S
 GONNA TURN OUT.

17:27.146 --> 17:29.119
NOBODY HAD A WORSE
 CHILDHOOD THAN ME,

17:29.119 --> 17:30.620
AND I TURNED OUT FINE.

17:30.620 --> 17:34.053
12 TIMES 12? 144.

17:34.053 --> 17:35.585
12 TIMES 13?

17:35.585 --> 17:38.358
HEY, WE´RE TALKING
 ABOUT YOU.

17:38.358 --> 17:40.130
SO, WHAT AM I GONNA DO?

17:40.130 --> 17:43.093
SIT IN MY ROOM
 FOR THE NEXT FOUR YEARS?

17:43.093 --> 17:45.835
NO, YOUR MOM HAD A POINT
 ABOUT JOINING A GROUP.

17:45.835 --> 17:48.368
YOU JUST HAVE TO PICK
 THE RIGHT GROUP.

17:48.368 --> 17:50.470
I MEAN,
 WHAT DO YOU LIKE TO DO?

17:50.470 --> 17:51.801
I DON´T KNOW.

17:51.801 --> 17:54.644
HEY, IF I KNOW
 MY LITTLE GIRL,

17:54.644 --> 17:59.509
IT´S PROBABLY BARBIES
 AND EASY-BAKE OVENS, HUH?

17:59.509 --> 18:03.253
MISS PAC-MAN, BETTY SPAGHETTY,
 BARREL OF MONKEYS.

18:03.253 --> 18:06.085
HELP ME OUT.

18:06.085 --> 18:07.817
I KIND OF LIKE WRITING.

18:07.817 --> 18:10.160
WELL, THERE´S GOT TO BE
 OTHER KIDS INTO THAT.

18:10.160 --> 18:11.561
THERE´S A POETRY CLUB,

18:11.561 --> 18:13.623
BUT I DON´T THINK MY POEMS
 WILL EVER BE GOOD ENOUGH.

18:13.623 --> 18:15.094
IF IT´S WHAT YOU LOVE,

18:15.094 --> 18:17.397
YOU GOT TO HAVE THE GUTS
 TO PURSUE IT.

18:17.397 --> 18:20.670
BESIDES, IF YOU WROTE THOSE
 POEMS, I´M SURE THEY´RE GREAT.

18:20.670 --> 18:22.432
CAN I READ ONE TO YOU?

18:22.432 --> 18:25.235
[ Groaning ] OHHH.

18:26.436 --> 18:28.778
OUT LOUD?

18:37.517 --> 18:39.289
WHAT´S UP?

18:42.121 --> 18:44.424
WHAT´S GOING ON
 IN THE KITCHEN?

18:44.424 --> 18:47.497
I THOUGHT WE SPRAYED
 FOR FREAKS.

18:47.497 --> 18:51.431
THAT´S THE POETRY CLUB.
 THEY´RE HAVING A PARTY.

18:51.431 --> 18:53.163
HOW DO I LOVE THEE?

18:53.163 --> 18:54.864
LET ME COUNT THE WAYS.

18:54.864 --> 18:56.366
[ BARKING ]
 Shh!

18:56.366 --> 18:58.568
Shh!

19:00.370 --> 19:01.911
HEY, GOOD FOR CARMEN.

19:01.911 --> 19:05.475
YEAH, WELL, SHE´S STILL
 BARELY TALKING TO ME.

19:05.475 --> 19:08.218
COME ON.
 YOU HAD THE RIGHT IDEA.

19:08.218 --> 19:09.619
YOU JUST HAD THE WRONG GROUP.

19:09.619 --> 19:11.921
YOU´RE A GREAT MOM,
 AND I´M NOT AFRAID TO...

19:11.921 --> 19:14.184
SEND IT OUT...
 TO THE WORLD.

19:14.184 --> 19:18.228
SEND IT OUT...
 TO THE WORLD.

19:18.228 --> 19:19.829
JUST SEND IT TO ME
 NEXT TIME,

19:19.829 --> 19:21.791
AND I´LL SEND IT OUT
 TO THE WORLD.

19:21.791 --> 19:23.493
I´M GONNA CLOSE THE SHADES.

19:23.493 --> 19:26.236
SOME OF MY FRIENDS
 ARE GETTING SKIN COLOR.

19:26.236 --> 19:28.438
DO YOU GUYS NEED
 ANY MORE BROWNIES?

19:28.438 --> 19:29.499
YEAH, ALL RIGHT.

19:31.771 --> 19:33.873
DID YOU HEAR THAT?
 "YEAH, ALL RIGHT."

19:33.873 --> 19:36.506
THAT´S NOT FAR FROM A
 "YOU´RE THE BEST MOM EVER.

19:36.506 --> 19:38.608
"JUST BECAUSE
 YOU DID ONE THING WRONG

19:38.608 --> 19:40.850
"DOESN´T MEAN I SHOULD
 FORGET THE MILLIONS

19:40.850 --> 19:42.782
OF WONDERFUL THINGS
 YOU´VE DONE."

19:42.782 --> 19:47.457
[ Imitating Bill Cosby ]
 THAT REMINDS ME OF A POEM --

19:47.457 --> 19:48.658
[ SIGHS ]

19:48.658 --> 19:51.891
ANGIE, WHEN IT COMES
 TO THE CHILDREN,

19:51.891 --> 19:54.193
WE´RE ON EQUAL FOOTING.

19:54.193 --> 19:58.728
NOW LET´S GO UPSTAIRS AND MAKE
 SOME SWEET, SWEET PUDDING.

19:58.728 --> 20:00.570
[ LAUGHS ]

20:03.973 --> 20:05.875
[ Spooky voice ] HEY!

20:05.875 --> 20:10.340
DON´T YOU KNOW NOT TO CHEW
 A BONE IN FRONT OF A SKELETON?

20:10.340 --> 20:13.343
THAT COULD BE MY ARM.

20:15.845 --> 20:18.248
DON´T GIVE ME THAT LOOK.

20:18.248 --> 20:20.350
YOU KNOW I CAN´T TAKE THAT.

20:20.350 --> 20:22.892
I MAY BE EVIL AND UNDEAD,

20:22.892 --> 20:25.995
BUT I LOVE DOGS.

20:25.995 --> 20:28.958
OOOOOH!

20:28.958 --> 20:33.463
NO, NOT THE LICKING!
 OOH, OOH!

20:33.463 --> 20:35.234
STOP THAT!

20:35.234 --> 20:37.737
IT TICKLES.

20:37.737 --> 20:42.011
OOH, A LITTLE MORE
 TO THE LEFT.

20:42.011 --> 20:47.277
YOU KNOW, AN ALTOID
 WOULDN´T KILL YOU.

